Hier sehen Sie die Dateisysteme die wie folgt unterstuetzt werden.

    FS     | bemerken | erstellen | kopieren | vergroessern | verkleinern | loeschen | Flags
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
linux-swap |    x     |    x      |    x     |      x       |      x      |     x    |   -
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ext2       |    x     |    x      |    x     |      x       |      x      |     x    |   x
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ext3       |    x     |    -      |    x     |      -       |      -      |     x    |   x
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
fat32      |    x     |    x      |    x     |      x       |      x      |     x    |   x
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
reiserfs   |    x     |    -      |    x     |      -       |      -      |     x    |   x
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
reiser4    |    -     |    -      |    x     |      -       |      -      |     x    |   x
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
xfs        |    x     |    -      |    x     |      -       |      -      |     x    |   x
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
